{"tid":1512870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online 其實有第二種玩法？","createTime":"2019-08-28T05:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:54:48.000Z","uid":307200,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"83a732e0627d2c589c767079835c8cd318b9d5d2","tid":1512870,"uid":307200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"Hi 雖然我係P牌仔 但希望大家睇睇呢個PO<br />\n<br />\n琴晚睇琴到招聘香城online 旗手既PO<br />\n跟著有個CM話建議整個 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衝</span></span> 既旗<br />\n諗諗下都唔係唔可行 話曬我地人數咁撚多<br />\n如果對面得果10-20個 面對我地只少50個 <br />\n50個都一齊衝既話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定驚撚到仆街</span><br />\n但重點只可以係對方人數少只可以衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望番依家 POPO跟本唔驚我地 <br />\n因為我地從來都冇主動進攻佢地<br />\n極其量只係玩火魔法 扔下磚<br />\n試問佢地又點會驚我地吖<br />\n<br />\n呢一切都係我琴晚訓覺發夢諗出黎<br />\n如果大家我鳩鳩地就由得個po沉啦"},{"pid":"f6df4bd76d71493167f556afc1219c97ded8a35a","tid":1512870,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=275d90f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=4e5dc55e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=b95d289b\" data-aut